contentrichtext.text: The '''Riverside Freeway''' is a named freeway in [[Orange County, California|Orange]], [[Riverside County, California|Riverside]], and [[San Bernardino County, California|San Bernardino]] Counties in the [[U.S. state]] of [[California]]. It consists of two segments: *[[California State Route 91]], from [[Interstate 5 in California|Interstate 5]] in [[Buena Park, California|Buena Park]] to [[California State Route 60]] in [[Riverside, California|Riverside]] *[[Interstate 215 (California)]], from [[California State Route 60]] in [[Riverside, California|Riverside]] to [[Interstate 10 in California|Interstate 10]] in [[San Bernardino, California|San Bernardino]] ==See also== *[[Riverside Expressway]], a highway in [[Brisbane]], [[Queensland]], [[Australia]] {{Roadindex}} [[Category:Southern California freeways]] [[Category:Named freeways in California]]
